platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 受賞歴のある冒険ゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 独創的な世界に飛び込もう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Frogmind’s follow-up to our 2013 iPad Game of the Year has our minds in apocalyptic overdrive. We can’t stop thinking about all the whirring blades, crushing boulders, and other deathtraps you have to fly, fall, and roll through. The physics-based puzzles are even more clever this time around, flowing from one to the next in sprawling, eerily beautiful levels laced with dread. Badland 2’s elegant controls and frequent checkpoints make it easy to pick up and love, but its wealth of missions and online challenges will wow even the most hardcore players.
